{"tid":1768889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個方法有冇得減低tvb收視？","createTime":"2019-12-04T11:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:18:20.000Z","uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"259c64c62ebafd8ad4eb98a9a62034c1552ad725","tid":1768889,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"宜家收視嘅計算方法：<br />\n<br />\n2018年，無綫電視、ViuTV、奇妙電視聯同香港11間廣告商會成員公司成立「香港電視觀眾收視調查創辦委員會」（FSC），並委任中國廣視索福瑞媒介研究（CSM）為2018年至2023年的香港電視觀眾收視調查機構。新監測方式則會分成「家中電視觀看」（In-home TV Viewing）及「網上觀看」（Online Viewing）兩種。前者將目標抽樣家庭由 800 個增加至 1,000 個，即是在該 1,000 個樣本家庭中安裝<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「個人收視記錄儀」</span></span>，並監測每個家庭的樣本成員所觀看的內容，包括免費電視或收視電視節目...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇方法可以自願安裝呢個記錄儀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地裝完再日日瘋狂睇viutv/港台31<br />\n咁就唔洗比tvb成日用果1000個盒黎打飛機<br />\n寧願晒幾舊水都唔要比佢賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d762bdf8e295cdbfd3b3923bff285db4707aa89","tid":1768889,"uid":321618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"我抽中左<br />\n佢會定期送幾百蚊俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我成年都唔睇一次電視 ..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f844b041ba323d8eeba25a0683445ebfc31270b8","tid":1768889,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d762bdf8e295cdbfd3b3923bff285db4707aa89","tid":1768889,"uid":321618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"我抽中左<br />\n佢會定期送幾百蚊俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我成年都唔睇一次電視 ..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"應該話 佢之前抽中左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382493fb4df5a5ff7848f3a21b1e801207137648","tid":1768889,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"好聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93244ad760a51abca9b7fe1c9ee84fc687c1d00","tid":1768889,"uid":281328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/03/hk-tv-audience-measurement2/wireless-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2Fhk-tv-audience-measurement2%2Fwireless-home%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDc0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=06df0216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/03/hk-tv-audience-measurement2/wireless-home/</a><br />\n<br />\n據 CSM 香港區總經理林立昇（Vincent）及 FSC 主席暨廣告媒體代理公司 phd 行政總裁黃國柱（Ray）表示，他們現正籌備招募監察的抽樣家庭，目標是收集到 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10,000 個志願家庭</span></span></strong>，並在 8 月從中抽出 800 戶具代表性的合適家庭，然後於 10 月開始進行監察，並目標在年底增至 1,000 戶，令總監察裝置達至約一萬個。之後就會在明年 1 月 1 號開始、每日提供收視數據，而抽樣家庭亦會每半年進行一次複檢，確保收集的數據更具認受性。"},{"pid":"a33d51335962a205d7d0dc6dbd184050205cfdb2","tid":1768889,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"259c64c62ebafd8ad4eb98a9a62034c1552ad725","tid":1768889,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"宜家收視嘅計算方法：<br />\n<br />\n2018年，無綫電視、ViuTV、奇妙電視聯同香港11間廣告商會成員公司成立「香港電視觀眾收視調查創辦委員會」（FSC），並委任中國廣視索福瑞媒介研究（CSM）為2018年至2023年的香港電視觀眾收視調查機構。新監測方式則會分成「家中電視觀看」（In-home TV Viewing）及「網上觀看」（Online Viewing）兩種。前者將目標抽樣家庭由 800 個增加至 1,000 個，即是在該 1,000 個樣本家庭中安裝<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「個人收視記錄儀」</span></span>，並監測每個家庭的樣本成員所觀看的內容，包括免費電視或收視電視節目...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇方法可以自願安裝呢個記錄儀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地